name: Listened to Chapter #29: You Can Call Me Al

content.html:
Orange Bowl BoysChapter #29: You Can Call Me AlShow NotesOne of our very favorite people in the college football space is the one and only Josh Pate! We are beyond thrilled that he decided to hang with us again. We covered a lot, including Josh and Ro meeting for the first time. Recruiting, Conf Realignment, Which Conf should the Canes be in? Does he have any worries about UF and FSU and their present classes in the 40’s? It was a great hour. We closed with 5 Questions as always.
